Scoring Framework

Use Scoring Framework to build and deploy propensity models for multiple Industries clouds use cases using clicks instead of code. Define template configurations for your scoring use cases to create CRM Analytics apps, Einstein Discovery models, and recipes.

Efficiently Debug Analytics App Installation Failures with Saved Assets
Maintain access to assets even if the analytics app installation fails to streamline issue identification and resolution. Save assets during installation to enhance debugging efficiency.
